  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to study the Development and Application of Rapid Nucleic Acid
      Diagnostic Kits for Clinical Specimens. Subjects are divided into two groups which are health
      group and Tuberculosis or lung cancer group in order to compare with the difference.
    </textblock>
